></div><div><span></span></div><div>Pro tip - hide the hands for a quicker easier painting</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gc4DNvT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>More ocean inspiration. Lots of playing in the waves. Which are pretty cold in San Diego tbh</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nn3OjwI.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>More shower shots! Love painting the water drips</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EX1AG66.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Convinced my friend to let me take photos of her mullet for my painting</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/24zeVs2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Had to get her tipsy so she was comfortable in front of the camera. This apartment had the more gorgeousssss light

Fp edit: wow first time on the front page! Send tasteful nudes you’d want me to paint! Thanks so much for the positive feedback, it’s encouraging me to break my two-year creative block. Also, feel free to check out more of my work here: https://devonbrowning.wixsite.com/devonbrowning</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ELLPYbZ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[flowerkid]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Mad Skillz</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/sSkyIBY</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kK3ksqX.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>If you know the original creator, please let me know so I can credit.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/sSkyIBY</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MeowMixWowmix]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Internet Gifts - Pt. 490</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/SDXlTs0</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IWLNJ7l.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>1.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wMWqJBe.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>2.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hr9AkJm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>3.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tQ7N4jf.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>4.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cCxm7j2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>5.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dRrXt37.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>6.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5Yz4FjV.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>7.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Fwiykz6.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><sp